title: Upload excel file to the Power Bi including the formulas
snippet:
Hi,
I have a commission spreadsheet which I want to replace and use the power bi.
The commission calculation is based on a tab in which I'm adding the amount collected on a monthly basis (see attached file).
Is it possible to load the formulas to Power BI module to upload and share online?
Please send me estimation for the time and the cost.

Thanks,
Rollo
